###
# Test Comments API

### Get all comments for a post (post ID 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/comments/post/1

### Get all comments for a post (post ID 2)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/comments/post/2

### Add a comment to a post (post ID 1)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/comments/post/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "content": "Great workout! Keep it up!"
}

### Add another comment to a post (post ID 1)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/comments/post/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "content": "Inspiring stuff, I need to try this!"
}

### Add a comment to a different post (post ID 2)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/comments/post/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "content": "Yoga is the best way to start the day!"
}

### Edit a comment (post ID 1, comment ID 5)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/comments/post/1/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Updated: This was an amazing workout!"
}

### Delete a comment from a post (post ID 1, comment ID 1)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/comments/post/1/1

### Delete a comment from a post (post ID 1, comment ID 2)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/comments/post/1/2
